      InstalledPackage is NOT retrieved or deployed. Managed packages
      (NPSP, Classy, FundraiseUp, etc.) are installed and upgraded via
      the setup UI or subscriber packaging API — never through this
      pipeline. A wildcard here attempts to "deploy NPSP" on every
      deploy, which fails. NPSP version pinning lives in `sfdx-project.json`.
    -->

